        <item>
          <versionCode>00</versionCode>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Postal Reform Act of</b> <b>2018</b></p> <p>This bill makes several changes to the organization and policies of the U.S. Postal Service. The bill includes provisions regarding health and retirement benefits, governance and operations, closures and consolidations of post offices, personnel policies, and contracting authority. </p>]]></text>
